OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Criminals are getting smarter at       
OL,6, targeting victims to gain access to    
OL,7, banking apps on mobile phones, a senior
OL,8, UK fraud officer has said.             
OL,10,FDetective Superintendent John Roch says
OL,11,Fthe technology behind the apps is      
OL,12,Fsecure but criminals are getting better
OL,13,Fat exploiting human behaviour.         
OL,15,FThieves typically "shoulder surf"      
OL,16,Fvictims to catch them entering their   
OL,17,FPIN before stealing the phone.         
OL,19,FThe financial impact of the crime can  
OL,20,Fbe enormous.                           
